olicy this led debate industry but no visible changes until march when electronic arts announced internally that was planning extend overtime pay some employees not currently eligible hasty hoffman later joined independent development studio 1st playable productions founded gamewatch website for discussing game-development environment industry-wide senior game developers age family responsibilities become more important many companies are moderating worst crunch-time practices attract better-quality staff see also list independent game developers list video game developers video game industry practices references bethke erik game development production texas wordware publishing inc p isbn 1-55622-951-8 mcguire morgan jenkins odest chadwicke cre ating gmes mechanics content technology wellesley massachusetts k peters p isbn 978-1-56881-305-9 bob ogo electronic game school teacher bates bob game design 2nd ed thomson course technology p isbn 1-59200-493-8 gnade mike july what exactly indie game indie game magazine retrieved january ahmed shahed naughty dog discusses being acquired by sony gamespot stream video games endless milwaukee journal pp business retrieved january video gaming headsets sound cards audio processors turtle beach retrieved b mckay brett mckay kate september so you want my job video game producer art manliness retrieved may ea human story from livejournal top gaming studios schools & salaries big fish games retrieved july game industry salary survey however different regions costs living will add wide range minimum maximum pay scales most larger developers such ubisoft will include profit-sharing plans royalty payments performance-related bonuses reward their employees from gamecareerguidecom game developer salary survey results are why crunch mode doesn't work lessons from igda game industry - pushcox from igda no fun for game developers from cnet news exemptions from minimum wage overtime from texas workforce commission california code regulation